{"tid":2490705,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–大哥哥......","createTime":"2021-04-15T21:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T21:19:18.000Z","uid":38861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27ef7ad283dcb23e9951b547a99a875ee4474aad","tid":2490705,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:16:56.000Z","msg":"自然法則下，大多數的不同物種均不能互相交配。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTrzYkR1DbVioaQDjCXeiCK1Y98wG3UPHtLBMhTozghpX?filename=OCLATNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCLATNp.jpg&h=6a8459d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管如此，近日有科學家「成功」嘗試把人類的幹細胞注入到猴子的胚囊裡頭，有部份的混種細胞更成功生存及繁殖19日之多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)從圖中可見，當人類的幹細胞注入到猴子的胚囊後，科學家便將「混種細胞」在體外的實驗室培植器皿飼養，並不斷觀察兩種細胞的繁殖去向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcbepdzy7Sqk3G65hgJX4Nwo2GxP5t21K1uGHW5Layiwz?filename=e4fpM7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4fpM7s.png&h=dd1bf658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)研究人員共嘗試注射人類幹細胞到132個猴子胚囊裡頭，隨著日數增加，胚胎的存活裡亦有所遞減。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS2knQiNsLM8XKUbeu4Fq8d8mNf8h8g8VhhHdant9Jxuv?filename=HP860sv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHP860sv.jpg&h=37cc4ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13日後，存活下來的胚胎僅只剩下3個。<br />\n<br />\n數字上無疑是一道失敗，但在整個過程中，人類的幹細胞的確是能夠在猴子胚囊繁殖及演化，證實人類幹細胞有能力在其他物種的胚胎細胞生存。<br />\n<br />\n為何要做這種實驗?<br />\n<br />\n初心是希望透過其他物種發展人體器官，作醫學治病用途。<br />\n現今已有不少研究在體外實驗室培植皿上發展類近器官的結構，但對比確實在動物體內的環境裡，效率及性能暫時來說始終是無法比得上。<br />\n<br />\n至於道德倫理方面，這研究無疑是對全世界人士的一道試探。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=a733a0da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=e337e1a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6015555/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6015555%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=446fa074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6015555/</a>"},{"pid":"3c7a73d67b7e5144909aebabd299de4346fcb9a5","tid":2490705,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fff42f65c8fc553e2b71da7860c302bb8edc04","tid":2490705,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T21:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵中東佬屌山羊咪得"}]}